data.description: Welcome Home to This 3bed , 1.5 bath 2 Story Home In Hamilton West! Enjoy a spacious front porch, 1st floor laundry, primary bedroom, and bathroom. Original 1900s charm wherever you look - (even still has the old pocket doors in tact). There is an eat in kitchen as well as an above ground Pool. The square footage on this home is amazing and feels even larger with the 10+ foot ceilings.
